title: There's a kind of cave fish that has lost its lateral line almost completely, and instead it's body is covered with what look like little joysticks, and are actually teeth. These it uses as sensors, because they cave it lives in floods so strongly that the other sensors that other fish use would be overwhelmed. It uses its mouth to sucker onto the wall and wait out the flood
pid: 129ab5a8-1b09-44a0-b3c3-147b55cd24b4
